  - verses:
    - title: "Hosea Announces Israel\u2019s Punishment"
      content: "O people of Israel,\n\tdo not rejoice as other nations do.\n\tFor
        you have been unfaithful to your God,\n\thiring yourselves out like prostitutes,\n\tworshiping
        other gods on every threshing floor.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "So now your harvests will be too small to feed you.\n\tThere will
        be no grapes for making new wine.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "You may no longer stay here in the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t\u2019s
        land.\n\tInstead, you will return to Egypt,\n\tand in Assyria you will eat
        food\n\tthat is ceremonially unclean.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "There you will make no offerings of wine to the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t.\n\tNone
