    - title: 
      content: "Assyria cannot save us,\n\tnor can our warhorses.\n\tNever again
        will we say to the idols we have made,\n\t\u2018You are our gods.\u2019\n\tNo,
        in you alone\n\tdo the orphans find mercy.\u201D  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "The <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps> says,\n\t\u201CThen I will heal you
        of your faithlessness;\n\tmy love will know no bounds,\n\tfor my anger will
        be gone forever.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "I will be to Israel\n\tlike a refreshing dew from heaven.\n\tIsrael
        will blossom like the lily;\n\tit will send roots deep into the soil\n\tlike
        the cedars in Lebanon.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Its branches will spread out like beautiful olive trees,\n\tas fragrant
        as the cedars of Lebanon.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "My people will again live under my shade.\n\tThey will flourish like
        grain and blossom like grapevines.\n\tThey will be as fragrant as the wines
        of Lebanon.  "
